nodes.text: Keri Lynn Russell (born March 23, 1976) is an American actress who portrays Zorii Bliss in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. She also starred in the 2014 sci-fi movie Dawn of the Planet of the Apes, with Andy Serkis.
